{"tid":2026471,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"重生的只呵唔鬧既樹窿Tg grp","createTime":"2020-05-21T03:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T14:25:57.000Z","uid":244876,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7f63fc2a7ad33ed545127d46c4a200fa27a72ba2","tid":2026471,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:30:09.000Z","msg":"曾經叫做只呵唔鬧既樹窿重生了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次為左比真係有需要既人真係有個窿去放負，求開解<br />\n重生之餘會整多左少少要求比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能會覺得咁樣做好麻煩，但係admin們都睇到係任意比大家入既結果就係會有好多人唔係真係想去幫人<br />\n而係去做好多野騷擾人，而始終人手有限好難逐一調停<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次會有張非常簡單既表格比大家填  我地好希望人來既係有需要被大家幫手又或者去幫下身邊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近期發生太多好負面既野，社會既情況好令人感到無力，失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬥黃情況甚多，灰心絕望都不在少數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔知以前個樹窿grp幫到幾多人  不過我個人就本住大家都係手足，大家都有需要幫忙既時刻<br />\n好似熊仔頭其中一條片咁  幫到人唔係令到自己開心 係想人地都開心<br />\n<br />\nlink就係到: 有需要就填一填交比admin<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/ko4G3auwF5yyYPvk7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fko4G3auwF5yyYPvk7&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPse2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=ba7982fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/ko4G3auwF5yyYPvk7</a><br />\n<br />\n係到都唔想講咩太沉重既野<br />\n希望大家仲記得過去發生既野，大家既付出同努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346bfdb376a9f075d96bba083b56a9483b4cae93","tid":2026471,"uid":330509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:34:21.000Z","msg":"有意義，幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e381a107cdf1dbbd91d4753c9e97f9a44c901b","tid":2026471,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"346bfdb376a9f075d96bba083b56a9483b4cae93","tid":2026471,"uid":330509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:34:21.000Z","msg":"有意義，幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝"},{"pid":"9dc0a09a2bd9141e89763f59cd2fcecc97144cbd","tid":2026471,"uid":330509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:38:31.000Z","msg":"大家同路人，真係要互相扶持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936ed9ad635adbe691b805d55b246a4423558421","tid":2026471,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T03:43:01.000Z","msg":"無錢又無力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有用時間去幫人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"