=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有需要就入來唔洗怕醜的"},{"pid":"856d8da3b2712329e29e7c8c81a1ed7782148853","tid":2026471,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:10:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"17f73720418cd0a7c1fcf362a622bc9b16d1c24a","tid":2026471,"uid":327585,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好心你地班admin就摺埋啦<br />\n成個谷都向到溝仔溝女又向到放閃，食唔到女/仔就向到搞事，搞唔掂就搵人出黎批鬥，根本就唔係幫人做人樹窿<br />\n又有一堆搞事搞非，無中生有既精神病人向到騷擾其他人<br />\n搞唔掂就識得潛水一排<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家個谷小人，無人講野覺得悶就走返出黎招人入"},{"pid":"73ca21358cc8ffe8d04cc2867d1d29f54db0f5a1","tid":2026471,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"17f73720418cd0a7c1fcf362a622bc9b16d1c24a","tid":2026471,"uid":327585,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好心你地班admin就摺埋啦<br />\n成個谷都向到溝仔溝女又向到放閃，食唔到女/仔就向到搞事，搞唔掂就搵人出黎批鬥，根本就唔係幫人做人樹窿<br />\n又有一堆搞事搞非，無中生有既精神病人向到騷擾其他人<br />\n搞唔掂就識得潛水一排<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家個谷小人，無人講野覺得悶就走返出黎招人入"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:21:17.000Z","msg":"以前係做得唔好<br />\n大家諗住唔鬧班人，只係呵人就得<br />\n<br />\n當然係唔掂啦<br />\n<br />\n本身對於個樹窿有無人氣有無人講野都唔太講究<br />\n<br />\nadmin都有d問題變左人手少在<br />\n<br />\n我知你屌緊個陣有班人係到想食女又癡線搗亂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係到收膠都認<br />\n以前大家唔識處理<br />\n<br />\n重生就係本住少少人咁幫下人<br />\n唔再係以前個種咩人都自由出入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你估大家想有咁多唔開心野發生咩"},{"pid":"1ba5618dfc8db3f17ed4b90de44718a1f508e411","tid":2026471,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T04:34:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b676602cc0e6c8de81785cd6798fc1714c51cb1f","tid":2026471,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:31:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8894b6074129531b290209a0a51447d6ebcbd27d","tid":2026471,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T06:28:44.000Z","msg":"我估有d巴絲可能會打錯tg 發現好耐都入唔到<br />\n可以再試下交多次from<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a037b5a96ce016c679cd1be3500511402b565626","tid":2026471,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:32:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8d48019f695e55ce8d61e3659022c5455e78d054","tid":2026471,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T07:46:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a75bc1b2d20ece34b74fce3fc2c6bedbb2330723","tid":2026471,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:07:44.000Z","msg":"推"}]}